BGL support for FTB based on zoid version 1.0-ZeptoOS-1.5-V1R3M2

Usage:
	1 Download zoid
	2 Copy ftb_agent to zoid directory
	3 Edit makefile in zoid directory & add ftb_agent as "BACKENDS"
	4 Go back to FTB directory and make
	5 Drop generated shared library file: ftb_agent_impl.so and
          ftb_agent_preload.so to lib directory under BGL_SITEDIST 
          (see zoid documentation for details)
        6 Compile compute code program with -lftb_blrts -lc and proper 
	  library path.


/*Note: will be mainly taken care of by configure script*/
